Yawa Weather!

Yawa! Weather is a simple Android Widget that give you the weather information about a location.
Yawa! Weather is possible thanks to Yahoo! Weather Api (a free Weather Api from Yahoo! http://developer.yahoo.com/weather/).
Yawa! Weather has the following features:

-> Very simple Widget that only shows the most important weather data

-> Updated Information about weather 

-> Simple to use, simple to understand

-> Supports several languages

-> Fast and Smart!


Download and enjoy!
